Future hopes:
    Add multiple transmitters
    Add individual totem selection
    Generally cleam up the code

Parts list:
    Totem - Arduino code - Tarim
    Streaming - Mikal Hart's Arduino Streaming library
    VirtualWire - Mike McCauley's RF transmission protocol
    proxy - Link port to USB serial device on Arduino transmitter
